{"tid":1620140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，反抗！","createTime":"2019-10-04T09:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T09:47:15.000Z","uid":162470,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f27bab27f7a10a6b1bb947f2dfd80302330d8004","tid":1620140,"uid":162470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:33:40.000Z","msg":"老豆搵仔講得啱：<br />\n唔好用咩宗教藉口去蒙面<br />\n咁樣除左係玩宗教之外<br />\n就係變相接受咗<br />\n從心底承認政府行呢條法例<br />\n或者代表你驚咗 所以先搵個理由比自己蒙面<br />\n咁同班狗唔打記者係咪全撚部都去扮記者 有咩分別？<br />\n點解要理由？抗爭就係唯一原因<br />\n包頭就包頭  唔撚洗宗教原因<br />\n而家係反抗呀<br />\n唔係畀你搵藉口去接受同埋逃避呀<br />\n搞清楚個心態先啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2X4Jwdy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2X4Jwdy.jpg&h=c942583f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aafd93b47de8c2d81e4860da41fda0f94875c4af","tid":1620140,"uid":56607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:34:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，革命！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"685f944258c05258fbf9c784e404cd5534f2adad","tid":1620140,"uid":162470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0e4c8e28a60701f6c623ac2c257f46137f7b7404","tid":1620140,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:34:51.000Z","msg":"革命是義務！"},{"pid":"3c6e95f2d191773b03059de5c59d660441c9cae6","tid":1620140,"uid":162470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:35:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8138fb5261057c379c311f0439edd93f81f59688","tid":1620140,"uid":324569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T09:35:57.000Z","msg":"1. 成立警衛公司，承接集會遊行期間真正保護市民工作，完全正當合理蒙面，「為人身安全而蒙面」<br />\n2. 逐步取代警隊<br />\n集思廣益！<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191004/large/1570176804_03ca.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%